ass=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704080/extras/606f91d42679f10f211e8243e4c8e6be.poster.avif?t=1728301071\" width=616 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704080/extras/606f91d42679f10f211e8243e4c8e6be.webm?t=1728301071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704080/extras/606f91d42679f10f211e8243e4c8e6be.mp4?t=1728301071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Craft</strong><br>You’ll need to craft different tools and solve quests to reach higher levels and face the spirit of the tree on top. You can craft swords, crossbows, shields, grenades, and grappling hooks to make your movement more efficient across the branches. Don't forget to use your Book of Crafts!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brace yourself for a brand new adventure in this strange world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704080/extras/4370d716809af0c444da0be2ff89d019.avif?t=1728301071\" width=616 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are truly excited that the third Stalk is available now as a free update. The Arctic level update adds even more content from additional weapons, enemies to fresh puzzles, a new boss, a unique temperature system, and a completely new environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
